[17/12/2016 22:48:07] <font color="#ff00ff">No, mientes.</font>
[17/12/2016 22:48:12] <font color="#00ff00">Espera.</font>
[17/12/2016 22:48:16] <font color="#00ff00">Que esperes te digo.</font>
